        <div class="clearfix" id="content-area">
         <div class="node node-type-page clearfix" id="node-57">
          <div class="content">
           <p>
            Thank you for your interest in donating to Columbia Community Service (CCS).
           </p>
           <p>
            <o:p>
            </o:p>
           </p>
           <p>
            Every year, faculty, staff and retirees from Barnard College, Columbia University and Teachers College use this opportunity to support soup kitchens, after-school programs, and other critical services through direct financial contributions. Employees can contribute using cash or credit card donations, or through payroll deductions. CCS welcomes matching gifts, stock transfers and bequests.
           </p>
           <p>
            Your donations are the key to the success of every Campaign. When you donate, we are able to assist human service agencies that are providing critical services in our local community.  With all three Schools covering the administrative expenses, 100% of all donations go directly to the grants that are awarded to CCS agencies.   Please give back to your neighbors by helping us grant forward with funding that is making a meaningful impact in our community.
           </p>
           <p>
            <o:p>
            </o:p>
           </p>
           <p>
            All employees and retirees, including Barnard College and Teachers College, can make a:
           </p>
           <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="/columbia-community-service-donation-payroll-pledge" style="font-size: 12.8px;">
             <img alt="" src="/files/communityservice/content/donationpage/payrollbutton.png" style="width: 240px; height: 28px;"/>
            </a>
            <a href="/columbia-community-service-donation-credit-card" style="font-size: 12.8px;">
             <img alt="" src="/files/communityservice/content/donationpage/credit_button.png" style="width: 240px; height: 28px;"/>
            </a>
            <span style="font-size: 11.8px;">
            </span>
           </p>
           <p>
            All check donations should be made payable to
            <strong>
             Columbia University
            </strong>
            and mailed to:
           </p>
           <div>
            Columbia Community Service
           </div>
           <div>
            Columbia University
           </div>
           <div>
            2980 Broadway
           </div>
           <div>
            Earl Hall, Room 304
           </div>
           <div>
            Mail Code 2025
           </div>
           <div>
            New York, NY 10027
           </div>
           <p>
            Please contact the CCS office at (212) 854-2387 or cm2891@columbia.edu to coordinate these contributions.  Thank you.
           </p>
           <p>
            <a href="/privacy-and-refund-policy">
             <strong>
              Privacy and Refund Policy
             </strong>
            </a>
           </p>
